<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Hello <%= @user.name %>,</h1>
    <p>This is a reminder that the following Todo has passed its due date:</p>
    <p><strong>Todo:</strong> <%= @todo.name %></p>
    <p><strong>Due Date:</strong> <%= @todo.due_date.present? ? @todo.due_date.strftime("%d %B %Y") : "no due date you can do whenever you want!!" %></p>
    <p>Please make sure to complete it as soon as possible.</p>
  </body>
</html>